---
title: "SAA 2019 Workshop: Transparent and Open Archaeological Research Using R"
categories:
  - Training
  - SAA2019
---

Register now for Transparent and Open Archaeological Research Using R, a workshop to be held at the Society of American Archaeology Annual Meeting in Albuquerque on April 10. If you're already registered for the meeting, you can still log in to [SAA.org](https://www.saa.org/annual-meeting/registration-info) to add this and any other workshops to your itinerary. 

More details are available at [https://benmarwick.github.io/2019-04-10-saa/](https://benmarwick.github.io/2019-04-10-saa/).

This workshop is brought to you by SAA's [Open Science Interest Group](https://osf.io/2dfhz/wiki/home/).
